                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <ph class="- topic/ph ">LED(s)
not illuminated</ph>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status and connection of the power supply.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Test the LEDs by pressing the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Indicator test button</b> on
the front panel to check if they illuminate.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check status of the device, see <xref href="HU250_Device_Overview_CPT_0000493476.dita"
                                    scope="local"
                                    type="concept"
                                    class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                        </sl>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <ph class="- topic/ph ">Canâ€™t connect with a PC to the HU250</ph>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the correct cable (straight Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection))
is used.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the cable is connected to the right LAN port (<b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">LAN right</b>).</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the local mode is enabled on the HU250.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the <b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">LAN right</b> port is active,
see <xref href="HU250_Network_Settings_CPT_0000493163.dita"
                                    scope="local"
                                    type="concept"
                                    class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                        </sl>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row platform="Modular-DC Modular-Inverter Modular-AC" class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <ph platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/ph ">No Modbus TCP/IP communication from the
NMC</ph>
                        <ph platform="Modular-DC Modular-Inverter Modular-AC" class="- topic/ph ">No Modbus
TCP/IP communication from the Modular controller</ph>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                           <sli platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/sli ">Check the status of the NMC card.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the correct cable (straight Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection))
is used.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the cable is connected to the right WAN port (<b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ETH1</b>).</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check that the <b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ETH1</b> port is active, see <xref href="HU250_Network_Settings_CPT_0000493163.dita"
                                    scope="local"
                                    type="concept"
                                    class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                           <sli platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" class="- topic/sli ">Check the IP configuration for the
WAN connection to the NMC, see <xref href="HU250_WAN_Settings_CPT_0000493473.dita"
                                    scope="local"
                                    type="concept"
                                    class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                        </sl>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <ph otherprops="IEC61850" class="- topic/ph ">No IEC communication</ph>
                        <ph otherprops="DNP3" class="- topic/ph ">No DNP communication</ph>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <sl class="- topic/sl ">
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status of the device, see <xref href="HU250_Device_Overview_CPT_0000493476.dita"
                                    scope="local"
                                    type="concept"
                                    class="- topic/xref "/>.</sli>
                           <sli class="- topic/sli ">Check the status of the Modbus communication, see the customized
LED <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Modbus status</b>.</sli>
                        </sl>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
